<section class="lp-section lp-section-dark a-fade-up" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag" style="text-align:center;">how it works</div>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 8px;">one email forward, one clear verdict. that's the whole loop.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 0;">perch. doesn't need your bank, your passwords, or your attention every day. just the emails you'd ignore anyway.</p>
    <div class="steps tilt-wrap">
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">01</span>
        <h3>forward it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">send us the renewal email, pdf, or screenshot. one forward, or batch a dozen in one go.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">02</span>
        <h3>we extract it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">our ai reads the provider, the amount, the renewal date, and the price change — even from scanned documents.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">03</span>
        <h3>you get a verdict</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">renew, cancel, or renegotiate — with a clear reason and the deadline. you decide what to do next.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">04</span>
        <h3>weekly digest</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">every monday morning, a 90-second summary of everything renewing this week. peace of mind in your inbox.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

